### Suppliers API Test Requests via Gateway

@gatewayUrl = https://localhost:7034
@token = your-jwt-token-here

### Get All Suppliers via Gateway
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/suppliers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Supplier by ID via Gateway
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/suppliers/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create New Supplier via Gateway
POST {{gatewayUrl}}/api/suppliers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "supplierName": "شركة الموردين المحدودة",
  "phone": "+966501234567",
  "email": "info@supplier.com",
  "address": "الرياض، المملكة العربية السعودية",
  "websit": "https://supplier.com",
  "countryId": 1,
  "supplierNote": "مورد موثوق"
}

### Update Supplier via Gateway
PUT {{gatewayUrl}}/api/suppliers/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "supplierName": "شركة الموردين المحدودة - محدث",
  "phone": "+966501234567",
  "email": "info@supplier.com",
  "address": "الرياض، المملكة العربية السعودية",
  "websit": "https://supplier.com",
  "countryId": 1,
  "supplierNote": "مورد موثوق - محدث"
}

### Delete Supplier via Gateway
DELETE {{gatewayUrl}}/api/suppliers/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Search Suppliers via Gateway
GET {{gatewayUrl}}/api/suppliers/search?name=شركة&email=supplier
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

